    <item>
      <title>墨西哥官员称海外投票可能需要更多预算</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-10/mexico-voting-abroad-may-require-bigger-budget-official-says</link>
      <description><![CDATA[负责该过程的官员表示，未来的墨西哥选举可能需要更大的预算，以避免公民在今年总统选举中遇到的海外投票问题。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-10/mexico-voting-abroad-may-require-bigger-budget-official-says</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 10 Jun 2024 22:03:18 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>工党将禁止向青少年销售高咖啡因能量饮料</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-10/labour-would-ban-sales-of-high-caffeine-energy-drinks-to-teens</link>
      <description><![CDATA[基尔·斯塔默 (Keir Starmer) 承诺，如果他领导的工党赢得下个月的英国大选，将禁止向青少年出售含高咖啡因的能量饮料，这是改善儿童身心健康的更广泛战略的一部分。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-10/labour-would-ban-sales-of-high-caffeine-energy-drinks-to-teens</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 10 Jun 2024 21:21:49 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>参议员称市场是墨西哥国会下一步行动的一个因素</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-10/usd-mxn-market-is-a-factor-in-mexico-congress-next-steps-monreal-says</link>
      <description><![CDATA[墨西哥参议院多数党领袖里卡多·蒙雷亚尔在接受采访时表示，墨西哥执政党在讨论宪法改革时将考虑市场因素。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-10/usd-mxn-market-is-a-factor-in-mexico-congress-next-steps-monreal-says</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 10 Jun 2024 20:41:04 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>联合国安理会通过美国支持加沙停火的决议</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-10/un-security-council-adopts-us-resolution-backing-gaza-cease-fire</link>
      <description><![CDATA[联合国安理会通过了美国起草的决议，批准了以色列与哈马斯战争的停火计划，这是华盛顿为保持双方都尚未完全承诺的提议的势头而进行的广泛活动的一部分。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-10/un-security-council-adopts-us-resolution-backing-gaza-cease-fire</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 10 Jun 2024 19:52:26 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>梅内德斯的合作者称他给了参议员的妻子 15,000 美元</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-10/menendez-collaborator-says-he-handed-15-000-to-senator-s-wife</link>
      <description><![CDATA[一名新泽西州商人告诉纽约联邦陪审团，他给了美国参议员罗伯特·梅内德斯的妻子一封装有 15,000 美元现金的信封，之后这位政客承诺将阻止州政府官员对一起刑事保险欺诈调查。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-10/menendez-collaborator-says-he-handed-15-000-to-senator-s-wife</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 10 Jun 2024 19:51:18 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>苏纳克因英国减税宣言面临保守党的强烈反对</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-10/sunak-faces-last-ditch-tory-revolt-over-uk-election-manifesto</link>
      <description><![CDATA[保守党宣言的早期草案引发了外界不安，人们担心该宣言缺乏可能避免保守党在英国大选中惨败的重大承诺。内阁大臣们在最后一刻呼吁里希·苏纳克 (Rishi Sunak) 在宣言中添加新的减税措施和更严格的移民政策。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-10/sunak-faces-last-ditch-tory-revolt-over-uk-election-manifesto</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 10 Jun 2024 15:49:58 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>亨特·拜登的辩护因枪支案而中断，无需证词</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-10/hunter-biden-defense-rests-in-gun-case-without-his-testimony</link>
      <description><![CDATA[亨特·拜登在特拉华州因枪支指控受审，陪审团未能就其在吸毒期间非法购买枪支的指控迅速做出裁决。他们预计将于周二恢复审议。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-10/hunter-biden-defense-rests-in-gun-case-without-his-testimony</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 10 Jun 2024 15:08:46 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>欧盟选举加剧政治风险 新兴货币下跌</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-10/emerging-currencies-drop-as-eu-elections-add-to-political-risks</link>
      <description><![CDATA[周一，大多数新兴市场货币兑美元走弱，波动性指标上升，因为随着极右翼在欧洲选举中的进展，政治风险成为焦点。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-10/emerging-currencies-drop-as-eu-elections-add-to-political-risks</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 10 Jun 2024 10:51:26 GMT</pubDate>
